<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<title>BSOD</title> 
		<hta:application 
		applicationname="BSOD"  
		version="2.0b" 
		maximizebutton="no" 
		minimizebutton="no" 
		sysmenu="no" 
		Caption="no" 
		windowstate="maximize"/>
		<style type="text/css">
			img {  
	  			width : 20%;  
	  			vertical-align:top;
				}
		</style>
	 
	</head>
	<body bgcolor="#0066FF" scroll="no"> 
		<font face="Arial" size="6" color="#FFFFFF">
			<br></br>
			<p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;">:(</p>
			<p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;">Your PC ran into a problem and needs to restart. We're just collecting</p> 
			<p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;">some error info, and then we'll restart for you.</p> 

			<progress id="file" max="100" value="70"><p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;"> 25% complete </p></progress>
		</font>
		<font face="Arial" size="3" color="#FFFFFF">
			<p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;"><img src="qr-code.png" width="20%">For more information about this issue and<br>possible fixes, visit<br>http://windows.com/stopcode</p>

			<p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;">If you call a support person, give them this info:</p>
			<p STYLE="padding:0 0 0 100px;">Stop code: CRITICAL_PROCESS_DIED</p>
		</font>
	</body>
</html>